13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>尺寸</h3>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 206px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 190.29126213592232%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"56\"\n        title=\"56\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/f547c2539a13103ec04d701595d642c4/a414c/56.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/f547c2539a13103ec04d701595d642c4/a414c/56.png 206w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 206px) 100vw, 206px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">56</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>U-Design 目前对Radio 单选区分了 3 次种尺寸：大（lg）、中（md）、小（sm）。</p>\n<h2 id=\"设计说明\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\" aria-label=\"设计说明 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设计说明</h2>\n<h3 id=\"选项不宜过多\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A\" aria-label=\"选项不宜过多 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>选项不宜过多</h3>\n<p>给用户的选择最好不要超过9个选项，否则建议使用下拉选择组件。</p>\n<h3 id=\"选项的排列应具有逻辑性\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%92%E5%88%97%E5%BA%94%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E6%80%A7\" aria-label=\"选项的排列应具有逻辑性 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>选项的排列应具有逻辑性</h3>\n<p>Radio单选 的选项应该按某种逻辑顺序排列，例如从最简单的操作到最复杂的操作、从可能性最大到可能性最小的，或者从最低风险到最高风险的，从而用户心理状态符合某种预期，帮助用户更好的理解表单。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAe0lEQVQI13WOuw7CMBAE8/+fSIVokACFKLbv6fOixIlTsc1or5jbydwRETiTKfCaHSk7mAWqG3UnHb0UHnezCmJFrd0xqdle2iH8fB23u+I9G3JhiDhS6lwTQbWCSLqIzgdyCUVtlC1LcjyejGU1iPQFYwkpIhr+pbWGH2c06w19SNFbAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"32\"\n        title=\"32\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/d76530153ecdfcef948af81db760e1cc/07a9c/32.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/d76530153ecdfcef948af81db760e1cc/f21e7/32.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/d76530153ecdfcef948af81db760e1cc/37523/32.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/d76530153ecdfcef948af81db760e1cc/07a9c/32.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/d76530153ecdfcef948af81db760e1cc/1acf3/32.png 1596w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">32</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"为用户提供较大的点击区域\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%BA%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F\" aria-label=\"为用户提供较大的点击区域 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>为用户提供较大的点击区域</h3>\n<p>根据费茨定律，目标越大，交互成本越低。单选按钮本质上很小，用户操作时很难点击到它们。U-Design 让用户不仅可以通过单击圆圈来选择选项，还可以通过单击文字来选择，以减小用户的操作成本。<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; ma